snippet.title: [PSP] K-On! Houkago Live!! - First Gameplay
snippet.description:
Now, let me put my PSP to a real recording session. I would have said that my love is a stapler, but I believe you have my stapler. *shotgunned*

And so that concludes gaming in September. Oh, I've still got to finish my playthroughs of those two superhero games... after I'm done with my first exam rush these next two days.

(I have a feeling that the thumbnails are working against me.)
